@startuml docker_gce_session_start
' セッション開始〜コンテナ生成のシーケンス図
title Docker on GCE — セッション開始〜コンテナ生成シーケンス

participant Browser
participant "cc-tunnel (Cloud Run)" as CloudRun
participant SessionManager as SM
participant PostgreSQL as DB
participant "GCE API" as GCEAPI
participant "GCE VM" as VM
participant "Docker Daemon" as Docker
participant "cc-remote-agent Container" as Container

Browser -> CloudRun: POST /api/conversations\n(新規会話作成)
CloudRun -> DB: INSERT conversation
CloudRun --> Browser: 201 Created {id, status: "idle"}

Browser -> CloudRun: POST /api/conversations/{id}/messages\n{content: "Hello"}
CloudRun -> SM: GetOrCreateEndpoint(conversation_id)

alt VM 稼働中 (warm)
  SM -> DB: SELECT session_endpoint\nWHERE conversation_id = ?
  note over SM: エンドポイント未登録 → 新規コンテナ作成
  SM -> Docker: docker run -d -p 909N:9091 cc-remote-agent
  Docker -> Container: コンテナ起動 (1-3秒)
  Container --> Docker: Ready
  SM -> DB: INSERT session_endpoint\n{conversation_id, vm_ip, port, status: "running"}
  SM --> CloudRun: Endpoint{ip: "10.128.0.5", port: 9093}
else VM 未稼働 (cold)
  SM -> GCEAPI: instances.insert\n(e2-standard-2, startup-script)
  note over GCEAPI,VM: VM 起動 30-60秒
  GCEAPI --> SM: {status: "RUNNING", internalIP: "10.128.0.5"}
  SM -> DB: INSERT vm_instance\n{ip, status: "running"}
  SM -> Docker: docker run -d -p 9091:9091 cc-remote-agent
  Docker -> Container: コンテナ起動 (1-3秒)
  Container --> Docker: Ready
  SM -> DB: INSERT session_endpoint\n{conversation_id, vm_ip, port}
  SM --> CloudRun: Endpoint{ip: "10.128.0.5", port: 9091}
end

CloudRun -> Container: POST /execute\n{prompt, session_id, ...}
Container -> Container: claude CLI 実行\n(ndjson streaming)
Container --> CloudRun: ndjson stream
CloudRun -> DB: UPDATE message\n(content_blocks, status)
CloudRun --> Browser: 202 Accepted

@enduml
